criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged ≥ 18 years;

          -  Diagnosis of clinically moderate to severe plaque-psoriasis;

          -  Initiating treatment with secukinumab during the identification period or within 30
             days prior to the index date;

          -  Patient agrees to sign the informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

        - Participation in any dermatology or rheumatology clinical trial, concurrent or within the
        last 30 days of the secukinumab initiating date
